7c2f048745a7f9becb","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"而家重有冇盆菜放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"盆菜有咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabf37a9782e84e4bb5416b448acf919d70351e4","tid":570200,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03dd37e948cd7cc8408e25f1512b93761554919d","tid":570200,"uid":87689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"伏到喊 食緊既時候檯面有隻小強爬過<br />\n嗌老闆黎 打死佐話冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:15:08.000Z","msg":".....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466a08d960562a1d89b38fb946f84e6ec0901f9c","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家重有冇盆菜放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>盆菜有咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n農場盆菜之家<br />\n 真係好__嬲<br />\nMichaelWong4844<br />\n等級1<br />\n2018-02-04<br />\n關注<br />\n開頭係門口諗住入去試下<br />\n我地揀左盆菜加火鍋 咁就七十五分鐘<br />\n點知野食無樣正常<br />\n一係好大浸雪味<br />\n一係就有&rsquo;宿&rsquo;味<br />\n連貢丸依一種咁普通嘅邊爐料都好難食<br />\n員工服務態度奇差<br />\n叫左四五次都唔應 明明個場得三四枱<br />\n係門口寫左 八十八蚊位<br />\n埋單嘅時候先話有 五六日 加二十蚊嘅收費<br />\n再外加醬油費 十蚊 野飲再另計<br />\n最後埋單百五蚊位<br />\n好食嘅話都無所謂 <br />\n問題係真係好__難食啊！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n以後請我都唔食<br />\n(以上食評乃用戶個人意見 , 並不代表OpenRice之觀點。)<br />\n用餐途徑<br />\n堂食<br />\n推介美食<br />\n一樣都無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/真係好-嬲-e2973103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Freview%2F%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD-%E5%AC%B2-e2973103&d=ofe%2BmqYPOb1lq9GThGjE0kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4ed3c43a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/review/真係好-嬲-e2973103</a>"},{"pid":"5eec80ee7d82eb90a0a09a39b0e3eac6a6d76c68","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"農場盆菜之家<br />\n<br />\n 羊腩煲幾好食<br />\nlovely chocolate<br />\n等級3<br />\n2018-01-07<br />\n關注<br />\n天氣又開始凍，突然好想食羊腩煲可以暖身，朋友介紹羊腩煲放題，就同fd黎試下<br />\n<br />\n原來除左羊腩煲，仲有串燒放題，或者可以羊腩煲加串燒。因為平時出去食羊腩煲都要2百幾，所以我地就決定試羊腩煲加串燒既放題<br />\n<br />\n串燒就得豬牛羊雞，仲有3款薯餅，雞脾同薯條，另外羊腩煲就可以任食羊。不過計返都係百幾蚊一個人，其實都好抵。食物都幾好食，我本身好鍾意食羊，佢個羊腩煲幾岩我口味<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有薯條好食過m記好多，粗身薯條黎，不過我掛住食唔記得影相<br />\n<br />\n我地無叫野飲，最後埋單都係304，計返150一個人，勁抵。<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static6.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic6.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg&h=7852c869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(以上食評乃用戶個人意見 , 並不代表OpenRice之觀點。)<br />\n用餐途徑<br />\n堂食4<br />\n味道3<br />\n環境3<br />\n服務3<br />\n衛生4<br />\n抵食<br />\n查看餐廳資料<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔乖呀 打手板</span>"},{"pid":"b76359be9163a2f3af92c48df098c4be3e210b99","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>農場盆菜之家<br />\n<br />\n 羊腩煲幾好食<br />\nlovely chocolate<br />\n等級3<br />\n2018-01-07<br />\n關注<br />\n天氣又開始凍，突然好想食羊腩煲可以暖身，朋友介紹羊腩煲放題，就同fd黎試下<br />\n<br />\n原來除左羊腩煲，仲有串燒放題，或者可以羊腩煲加串燒。因為平時出去食羊腩煲都要2百幾，所以我地就決定試羊腩煲加串燒既放題<br />\n<br />\n串燒就得豬牛羊雞，仲有3款薯餅，雞脾同薯條，另外羊腩煲就可以任食羊。不過計返都係百幾蚊一個人，其實都好抵。食物都幾好食，我本身好鍾意食羊，佢個羊腩煲幾岩我口味<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有薯條好食過m記好多，粗身薯條黎，不過我掛住食唔記得影相<br />\n<br />\n我地無叫野飲，最後埋單都係304，計返150一個人，勁抵。<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static6.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic6.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg&h=7852c869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(以上食評乃用戶個人意見 , 並不代表OpenRice之觀點。)<br />\n用餐途徑<br />\n堂食4<br />\n味道3<br />\n環境3<br />\n服務3<br />\n衛生4<br />\n抵食<br />\n查看餐廳資料<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔乖呀 打手板</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static5.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YS7EFB275FA48990D2mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic5.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YS7EFB275FA48990D2mx.jpg&h=574932fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4f9329eb4dbd91da18a97e1891cd9ee4618cfa","tid":570200,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"啲雞好似雪咗十幾廿年咁，老到仆街又勁大雪味，貼埋錢俾我食多次都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3bba4744998b47ea5414008aba91321f88d664","tid":570200,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b76359be9163a2f3af92c48df098c4be3e210b99","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>農場盆菜之家<br />\n<br />\n 羊腩煲幾好食<br />\nlovely chocolate<br />\n等級3<br />\n2018-01-07<br />\n關注<br />\n天氣又開始凍，突然好想食羊腩煲可以暖身，朋友介紹羊腩煲放題，就同fd黎試下<br />\n<br />\n原來除左羊腩煲，仲有串燒放題，或者可以羊腩煲加串燒。因為平時出去食羊腩煲都要2百幾，所以我地就決定試羊腩煲加串燒既放題<br />\n<br />\n串燒就得豬牛羊雞，仲有3款薯餅，雞脾同薯條，另外羊腩煲就可以任食羊。不過計返都係百幾蚊一個人，其實都好抵。食物都幾好食，我本身好鍾意食羊，佢個羊腩煲幾岩我口味<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有薯條好食過m記好多，粗身薯條黎，不過我掛住食唔記得影相<br />\n<br />\n我地無叫野飲，最後埋單都係304，計返150一個人，勁抵。<br />\n <img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YQ6A0D6D46532BD381mx.jpg&h=0cdfab8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static6.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic6.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YTB27DFCCCF07329A3mx.jpg&h=7852c869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(以上食評乃用戶個人意見 , 並不代表OpenRice之觀點。)<br />\n用餐途徑<br />\n堂食4<br />\n味道3<br />\n環境3<br />\n服務3<br />\n衛生4<br />\n抵食<br />\n查看餐廳資料<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔乖呀 打手板</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static5.orstatic.com/userphoto/photo/O/JFL/03U6YS7EFB275FA48990D2mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic5.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto%2Fphoto%2FO%2FJFL%2F03U6YS7EFB275FA48990D2mx.jpg&h=574932fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"正正常常食過羊腩雞煲算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53e2d4c5260e9da78341bfec156a1555b662ec5","tid":570200,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4f9329eb4dbd91da18a97e1891cd9ee4618cfa","tid":570200,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"啲雞好似雪咗十幾廿年咁，老到仆街又勁大雪味，貼埋錢俾我食多次都唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b3e51c91042d667c015556f1bd07cd27501ee3","tid":570200,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:08:47.000Z","msg":"你老母生愛滋，你男朋友生花柳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89ae5790635dfda4f0ce8cab3639de18b5b5cc1","tid":570200,"uid":87517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"睇comment都知講緊邊間 伏到仆街 上次係果度食完雞煲瀉足一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fc4100ac5fb4bd715a8e024183dc73d053c307","tid":570200,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"真不知所謂<br />\njackyjacky3513<br />\n等級1<br />\n2018-02-08<br />\n關注<br />\n小心D菜和其他收費，非常唔清楚<br />\nD食物質素十分唔掂，D態度完全無<br />\n羊肉和雞唔好食，串燒烤到雞牛豬一樣味，羊串完全不能放入口， 我十個人座位窄到不能接受 啲食物食完又唔嚟執碟 三催四請先來<br />\n(以上食評乃用戶個人意見 , 並不代表OpenRice之觀點。)<br />\n用餐途徑<br />\n堂食<br />\n--味道<br />\n1環境<br />\n1服務<br />\n1衛生<br />\n--抵食"},{"pid":"a77c7045206c920196d1d948e7a5ecaaf189882e","tid":570200,"uid":13977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚食 難食到仆街 d串燒明顯叮熱 <br />\n所有野都係暖 唯一可取係炸野 <br />\n雞煲一黎就黑既 想比錢食屎可以試下<br />\n上次食完 一人要130蚊埋單 <br />\n仲要去茶記再食野先掂<br />\n估唔到tvb收錢做間咁難食既垃圾打手"},{"pid":"10955a1fa9cde57bd55f24b10599956a15fa7b50","tid":570200,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77c7045206c920196d1d948e7a5ecaaf189882e","tid":570200,"uid":13977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚食 難食到仆街 d串燒明顯叮熱 <br />\n所有野都係暖 唯一可取係炸野 <br />\n雞煲一黎就黑既 想比錢食屎可以試下<br />\n上次食完 一人要130蚊埋單 <br />\n仲要去茶記再食野先掂<br />\n估唔到tvb收錢做間咁難食既垃圾打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2322367ddb81f8361a0b64b14c2ad896681e00","tid":570200,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f6baed0596d5ff51bff7a64da480497000a8ee8","tid":570200,"uid":169819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"食過一次，雞煲+串燒。雞煲一開始個煲會有其他料例如菜， 之後剩係會加雞比你。<br />\n任食係無限round,  飲料好似十蚊到一罐，食物質素普通，但我食地果時醬油費20蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/200608_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F200608_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7478de3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/200622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F200622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cb5c6aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/200630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F200630_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=613bc941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有食過28蚊雞煲，但上面果班才是打手<br />\n尤其係唔係都吹有老鼠<br />\n呢個版幾乎係帖都質落去，過分！<br />\n<br />\n真正伏位：<br />\n一，選辣係超勁麻辣<br />\n  格籬有人選辣，食唔夠2舊要飲成罐汽水<br />\n  最後差不多1人點咗3罐汽水才頂得順<br />\n  所以想食就一定選唔辣<br />\n二，第一round如圖，件件骨頭多過肉<br />\n  實際上要食半粒鐘才輪完第一round<br />\n  之後加雞才有返啲似樣的肉<br />\n  輪完既骨夠半個煲<br />\n  但要煮返5分鐘才可以食<br />\n  所以實際只是添咗2round雞，共3round<br />\n  理論平手離場，上面計埋雜費加一<br />\n  實際42蚊/位<br />\n三，75分鐘趕收工咁<br />\n  食野講享受，就算任食都有得施施然嚐味<br />\n  但明顯去咗戰場<br />\n  輪骨令全件事變晒質<br />\n  先前我去食另一間蒸鍋，淨50分鐘慢慢歎粥<br />\n<br />\n雖然無即場叫飲品<br />\n但離開後，飲足2罐才解渴<br />\n反而開頭一人2隻鮑魚仔才覺得有點特色<br />\n<br />\n呢期睇埋價錢零興趣<br />\n108蚊的話，屋邨酒樓任食火煱都大把選擇<br />\n使鬼特登塔車入黎食"}]}